Privacy Policy
Minicades Mobile is committed to protecting the privacy of our players. This privacy policy describes how Minicades Mobile uses and protects any information that you give us when you play any of our games. Should we ask you to provide certain information by which you can be identified when using our games, you can be assured that it will only be used in accordance with this policy. Minicades Mobile may change this policy from time to time by updating this page. You should check back from time to time to ensure that you are happy with any changes.
What we collect
We may collect the following information when you play our games:
Your location (country/city only).
The type of device you’re using.
Your game play statistics.
Advertising statistics.
Advertising ID
The advertising ID is a unique, user-resettable ID for advertising, provided by the mobile device’s operating system. We may use this ID to enhance serving and targeting capabilities, re-target specific campaigns, or pass on the ID to our partners, including third-party advertisers. Advertising ID does not reveal any information about the User or his or her device. If you prefer to opt out or reset your advertising ID, please follow these standard instructions:
iOS –
Opt out of interest-based ads in the App Store and Apple News
Android –
Opt out of seeing personalized ads
Third-party advertising
We may use, store, and share with third-party advertisers certain technical information (including IP addresses and advertising IDs) or aggregated information of the users of Minicades Mobile’s Services such as general demographic and preference information. We may also allow advertisers to collect such technical or aggregate information that they may share with us. Such information collected may be used for industry analysis, demographic profiling, and to deliver targeted advertising.
